sense.commentary:
Syntax includes: NP1[agent] BUTT NP2[theme]
NP1[agent] BUTT NP2[theme 1] PP {NP[theme 2]}
Note: this sense seems to be restricted to the domain of wood-working.

Synax includes: NP1[agent] BUTT_IN 
NP1[agent] BUTT_IN PP {on NP[patient]}
Is: butt in

Syntax includes: NP1[agent] BUTT_OUT
NP1[agent] BUTT_OUT PP {of NP[patient]}
Is: butt out
